aVIf you are asked to estimate
p118
aVthe walking speed of a man in a video, for example,
p119
aVyour answer will be different if you're told to think about cheetahs or turtles.
p120
aVA hill appears steeper if you've just exercised,
p121
aVand a landmark appears farther away
p122
aVif you're wearing a heavy backpack.
